member.name: T:DroneDelivery.Mobile.Services.ApiClient
member.summary: Client HTTP "real". Cand backend-ul nu e pornit, vei primi erori de retea (capturable in VM). Pentru a rula aplicatia fara backend, in MauiProgram se inregistreaza in DEBUG un MockApiClient.

member.name: T:DroneDelivery.Mobile.Services.MockApiClient
member.summary: Backend fake in-memory. Scop: aplicatia sa mearga complet (navigare + CRUD) fara API real.

member.name: T:DroneDelivery.Mobile.Services.SwitchableApiClient
member.summary: Alege dinamic intre backend real si mock, pe baza preferintei "UseMockBackend". Astfel aplicatia poate porni fara API, dar poti comuta pe URL real fara rebuild.
